node.text:
After moving from strongman to boxing it was important for me to consider the stack of supplements I was using.  My training has changed a lot so I turned to @transparentlabs lineup to keep me fuelled as effectively as they did during my World Record Deadlift training.   @transparentlabs has launched both The Mountain Pack and World’s Strongest Stack on www.transparentlabs.com/hafthor  Use the Code: THOR72 to save 20% for the next 72hours  To learn more about the World’s Strongest Stack head over to @transparentlabs where I take you through both of my stacks 

  #transparentlabs #TLmakingitcount 
#worldsstrongeststack #mountainpack
#supplements

node.text: Most of you know I tested positive for covid-19 last week. I’ve been feeling much better so I wanted to see how many push-ups I could do in a row. Check out the video
Now, it’s your turn to build your own Viking legend on #assassinscreedvalhalla #likeaviking
